latestPosts.caption:
There’s something about a cotton saree or as we call it in UP, a suti saree that just feels like home. Effortlessly elegant, gently hugging the body, and oh-so-comfy.
It reminds me of my mom, her warmth, and those summer days wrapped in soft cotton drapes. 🌸
Wearing these beautiful sarees from @ke.sari.ka — a brand close to my heart, run by a fellow fauji wife. 💛

Shot by : @im_clickman 

[ fauji wife, cotton saree, elephant, strolling in the city, saree love]
